    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create your Hero's Journey</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo, you won’t just play—you’ll create. The world of Obu becomes a sandbox for your imagination as you design and customize your own character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/extras/f5782d2f3fd47365a7d4e49a0f1afcf7.poster.avif?t=1759972482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/extras/f5782d2f3fd47365a7d4e49a0f1afcf7.webm?t=1759972482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/extras/f5782d2f3fd47365a7d4e49a0f1afcf7.mp4?t=1759972482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover your Hero's potential</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Obu</i> combines fast-paced combat and exploration. In addition to customizing your character, you'll dive into action-packed battles, harness mana, and build everything from weapons to vehicles. The demo introduces you to the core mechanics, combat and powerups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/extras/15003dd4b015b60b2e9b10e7d916caa7.poster.avif?t=1759972482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/extras/15003dd4b015b60b2e9b10e7d916caa7.webm?t=1759972482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/extras/15003dd4b015b60b2e9b10e7d916caa7.mp4?t=1759972482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
